d-public-access-to-popular-beach-claims-he-owns-the-road-the-beach-and-the-tides/?share=email" target="_blank" title="Click to email this to a friend"><span></span></a></li><li class="share-print"><a rel="nofollow" class="share-print sd-button share-icon no-text" href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/05/29/silicon-valley-billionaire-who-blocked-public-access-to-popular-beach-claims-he-owns-the-road-the-beach-and-the-tides/" target="_blank" title="Click to print"><span></span></a></li><li class="share-end"></li></ul></div></div></div>
