ick to email this to a friend"><span></span></a></li><li class="share-print"><a rel="nofollow" class="share-print sd-button share-icon no-text" href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/05/01/is-the-credit-bubble-popping-carlyle-group-warns-on-frothiness-and-junk-bond-deals-get-pulled/" target="_blank" title="Click to print"><span></span></a></li><li class="share-end"></li></ul></div></div></div>
